key.description: Target type. Valid values are `Cluster` (EKS Cluster), `Clusters` (ECS Clusters), `DBInstances` (RDS DB Instances), `Instances` (EC2 Instances), `Nodegroups` (EKS Node groups), `Roles` (IAM Roles), `SpotInstances` (EC2 Spot Instances), `Subnets` (VPC Subnets), `Volumes` (EBS Volumes) , `Pods` (EKS Pods), `Tasks` (ECS Tasks). See the [documentation](https://docs.aws.amazon.com/fis/latest/userguide/actions.html#action-targets) for more details.

value.description: Target name, referencing a corresponding target.
